.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt BDFMOTD 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm bdfmotd
.Nd Generate a figlet art to use in motd
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl dhV
.Ar string
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility generates an ASCII art version of the string
.Ar string
using
.Xr figlet 1 .
It is preconfigured to use the contessa font.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl d
Enable debug mode.
.It Fl h
Print usage and quit.
.It Fl V
Print version and quit.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr figlet 1
.Xr motd 1
